snippet.textDisplay:
Theme is the heart of Lyrics or a song.... and also the music depends on the theme I guess.

And I think the theme should not be change or blend or mixed up with any other factor.
Because as a transcendentalist Lalon was a great romantic poet and composer in the literature world. His deed was worthy concert of the anthem about The Creator .
His work is truly Perennial then any other.
And undoubtedly, there is none in the world hadn't expressed this level of High Dimensional Wisdom Literature about #Creator (God) yet in 500 years.
Though if there is any incredulous, you can sensibly analyse.

Topollogically constituent of the lyrics of Lalon is rejoinder of Socratic's 1st philosophical thoughts (Wisdom) too.

So please attention about that.... the theme and flavour should not be change or faded out.
